{"tid":1354464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫推] 嚴正呼籲各區警察切勿繼續警黑勾結","createTime":"2019-07-23T06:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:40:03.000Z","uid":278201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e65195bb00c6a5452b50281de0d46feca64516a8","tid":1354464,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"再次sorry for p牌仔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">現正呼籲各區前線警察切勿再一意孤行，違心與黑警勾結，服從無理指令。本人相信部分警察尚有良知，請與新界區黑警分明立場，請按章工作，僅以合理、合法及洽當武力執法。<br />\n<br />\n請緊記警察誓詞：</span><br />\n本人（姓名），謹以至誠作出宣言（或，謹向全能之主發誓），本人會竭誠依法為香港特別行政區政府效力為警務人員，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遵從、支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律</span></span>，以不畏懼、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人</span></span>及忠誠、努力的態度行使職權，執行職務，並且毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的一切<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">合法</span></span>命令。<br />\nSource:  香港法例232章 《警隊條例》附表1"},{"pid":"b65f2477259421a69a16e5d232a73d0580c69f2f","tid":1354464,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:51:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"866ec36bc4dbfda20f70b94932459f98cfbad8c3","tid":1354464,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:54:18.000Z","msg":"轉載俾你啲同袍睇 唔好俾人睇死你地全部都係毅進仔 死黑警"},{"pid":"0f415896d87c0bea5b69fa6d94241fa9dbde360b","tid":1354464,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aae61e7f201fa9c5b0332329d0b7ab23e1020a33","tid":1354464,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dac6ec162cb79d377ea191c12b46a6e41ace3d86","tid":1354464,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:55:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00cab42e8077b64af713f2820354958b3824e62a","tid":1354464,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e65195bb00c6a5452b50281de0d46fe